{"tid":1459144,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］和理飛機場輪更制","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T06:01:30.000Z","uid":121290,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4efe320be6f2f4832501a0badd19b98d8a526976","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"唔知work唔work<br />\n大家再比下意見<br />\n<br />\n如果想長期攤緩機場，建議行shift制<br />\n<br />\n當大家好想日日去機場癱瘓運作，但呢樣係長期作戰，如果weekday要入去機場，正常打工仔未必個個有本錢日日去玩，同埋要癱瘓機場，其實大約十零萬人左右已經夠做，好似812今日咁，咁多人入黎都係人塞人，如果可以做到行shift制，咁就巴絲們可以一星期只係請一兩次半日嘅annual leave, sick leave已經可以去癱瘓機場<br />\n有個建議係：如果個shift係用身份證尾數黎分，例如：<br />\n身份證尾數係0,1(Monday), 2,9(Tue), 3,8(Wed), 4,7(Thu), 5,6(Fri)，星期六、日就自由選擇<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以做到maximise Human Resources, 又唔會好似變左估領運動變尻佔咁"},{"pid":"885dc3f8ae5da342bce5f1025197eae4b89c4cce","tid":1459144,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"a682385b8837f537f42a16f3264735b13baccc13","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"953a97f808ccdd37f889f3c1344117d05faa5c90","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:07.000Z","msg":"*癱瘓"},{"pid":"7ba2ddfdd00e88a9addc47a6351718827733b78f","tid":1459144,"uid":222581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a614df3788975ec8780c471e3cb41b45bda141b","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b75f6b463de67b9f158314a22c85ab2bd182aaf","tid":1459144,"uid":74764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1905fe27d44aab86994a1d0c45dd73d47413d7c3","tid":1459144,"uid":139200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"唔夠人文宣<br />\n夠人就癱瘓"},{"pid":"195628e132d0cfffc9088e749335178c217887d8","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1905fe27d44aab86994a1d0c45dd73d47413d7c3","tid":1459144,"uid":139200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"唔夠人文宣<br />\n夠人就癱瘓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"今日夠人<br />\n但未必要下下動用咁多人"},{"pid":"da4249429b930e2cc79507a79353632a8433a90e","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:25:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c22629820d3b3b87cac32c34c037a82f137d84c3","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"277593e58042c63cda92d9473ff330b6c79d7a89","tid":1459144,"uid":130521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"標題： ［機場發夢第二步］喬裝旅客行動正式啟動<br />\n<br />\n琴日發夢去左機場 癱瘓左機場運作 <br />\n算是第一步成功左 <br />\n<br />\n要行第二步了 應該點樣繼續發個好夢呢<br />\n<br />\n頭先我又食藥訓覺<br />\n我夢見機場每日輪流都幾萬人迫爆 <br />\n呢幾萬人扮成旅客 冇人著黑衫 冇人衝擊 <br />\n警犬跟本分唔到旅客定發夢人士<br />\n冇人被捕 冇人受傷 但經濟繼續癱瘓 <br />\n原來最大既人質就係機場<br />\n<br />\n1. 請喬裝成旅客 拎警犬冇權力驅散<br />\n2. 請持之以恆  每日輪流去發夢癱瘓航空<br />\n3. 文宣組繼續出文 推廣發夢計劃2.0<br />\n<br />\n請大家推post 同share此方案<br />\n犬隻可以喬裝 我地都可以喬裝<br />\n<br />\n以卵擊石  只能敗走！"},{"pid":"857f92a23aead4ded8a9bb58ef921cd87fd3a312","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64818e8506f0f7bcf48a0592aa73bd95dfd97320","tid":1459144,"uid":121290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c89c22926f0959b3509